{"name": "deepfos-ipc", "metadata": {"name": "deepfos-ipc", "version": "1.3.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["loguru"], "summary": "DeepFOS interprocess communication protocol", "upload_time": 1733724434}, "documentation": ["## \u4ecb\u7ecd\r\n\r\n\u672c\u9879\u76ee\u63d0\u4f9bPython\u8fdb\u7a0b\u95f4\u901a\u4fe1\u7684\u57fa\u7840\u529f\u80fd\uff0c\u9002\u7528\u4e8e\u591a\u8fdb\u7a0b\u7f16\u7a0b\u4e2d\u4e00\u4e3b\u591a\u4ece\u7684\u7f16\u7a0b\u6a21\u578b\u3002\r\n\r\n\u9879\u76ee\u4e2d\u7684Server\u53ef\u5728\u4e3b\u8fdb\u7a0b\u542f\u52a8\uff0cClient\u5728\uff08\u591a\u4e2a\uff09\u5b50\u8fdb\u7a0b\u4e2d\u542f\u52a8\uff0c\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u53d1\u9001\u7684\u6d88\u606f\u80fd\u591f\u88ab\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u63a5\u6536\uff0c\r\n\u5e76\u4e14\u5bf9\u4e8e\u4e0d\u540c\u7684\u6d88\u606f\u7c7b\u578b\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u6ce8\u518c\u4e0d\u540c\u7684\u56de\u8c03\u903b\u8f91\u3002\r\n\u9879\u76ee\u9884\u7f6e\u4e86\u4e00\u4e9b\u5e38\u7528\u901a\u4fe1\u534f\u8bae\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u4e5f\u63d0\u4f9b\u7b80\u4fbf\u7684\u81ea\u5b9a\u4e49\u901a\u4fe1\u534f\u8bae\u7684\u63a5\u53e3\u3002\r\n\r\n\u8fdb\u7a0b\u95f4\u901a\u4fe1\u5728unix\u64cd\u4f5c\u7cfb\u7edf\u4f7f\u7528unix socket\u5b9e\u73b0\uff0c\u5728windows\u7cfb\u7edf\u4e2d\u4f7f\u7528tcp connection\u3002\r\n\r\n##  Quick Start\r\n\r\n1. \u542f\u52a8\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfrom dip import Server\r\nimport asyncio\r\n\r\ndef cb(req, mtype, data):\r\n    print(data['hello'])\r\n\r\nserver = Server('/tmp/run.sock', callback=cb)\r\nasyncio.run(server.serve_forever())\r\n```\r\n\r\n2. \u4f7f\u7528\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u53d1\u9001\u6d88\u606f\r\n```python\r\nfrom dip import Client\r\n\r\ncli = Client('/tmp/run.sock')\r\ncli.send_json({'hello': 'world'})\r\n```\r\n\r\n\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u5c06\u4f1a\u8f93\u51fa\r\n```python\r\n>>> 'world'\r\n```\r\n\r\n## \u81ea\u5b9a\u4e49\u901a\u4fe1\u534f\u8bae\r\n\r\n\u5982\u679c\u9700\u8981\u81ea\u5b9a\u4e49\u8fdb\u7a0b\u95f4\u901a\u4fe1\u65f6\u4f20\u8f93\u5b57\u8282\u6d41\u7684\u683c\u5f0f\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u4f7f\u7528\u81ea\u5b9a\u4e49`Protocol`\r\n\r\n```python\r\nimport typing\r\nfrom dip import Protocol\r\n\r\nclass NewProtocol(Protocol, mtype=b'N'):\r\n    @classmethod\r\n    def decode_body(cls, buf: bytes) -> typing.Any:\r\n        pass\r\n    \r\n    @classmethod\r\n    def encode_body(cls, data: typing.Any) -> bytes:\r\n        pass\r\n```\r\n\r\n\u81ea\u5b9a\u4e49\u901a\u4fe1\u534f\u8bae\u9700\u8981\u4f7f\u7528\u4e00\u4e2abyte\u4f5c\u4e3a\u6807\u8bc6\uff08mtype\uff09\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u5fc5\u987b\u5b9e\u73b0`decode_body`\u548c`encode_body`\u4e24\u4e2a\u65b9\u6cd5\u3002\u5176\u4e2d:\r\n\r\n> 1. `encode_body` \u7528\u4e8e\u5c06python\u5bf9\u8c61\u5e8f\u5217\u5316\u4e3a\u5b57\u8282\u6d41\r\n> 2. `decode_body` \u7528\u4e8e\u5c06\u5b57\u8282\u6d41\u53cd\u5e8f\u5217\u5316\u4e3apython\u5bf9\u8c61\r\n\r\n\u4e24\u8005\u4e00\u822c\u4e92\u4e3a\u9006\u64cd\u4f5c\uff0c\u5373\u5bf9\u4e8epython\u5bf9\u8c61`obj`\uff1a\r\n\r\n```python\r\nobj == Protocol.decode_body(Protocol.encode_body(obj))\r\n```\r\n*\u6ce8: \u8fd9\u5e76\u4e0d\u662f\u786c\u6027\u89c4\u5b9a\uff0c\u53ea\u662f\u4e00\u79cd\u901a\u5e38\u505a\u6cd5*\r\n\r\n\u4e0b\u8ff0\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u975e\u5e38\u7c97\u7cd9\u7684\u56fa\u5b9a\u5b57\u7b26\u4e32\u538b\u7f29\u534f\u8bae\u7684\u5b9e\u73b0\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfrom dip import Protocol\r\nfrom dip import errors\r\n\r\nclass StringMappingProto(Protocol, mtype=b'S'):\r\n    MAP = {\r\n        'Hello World': b'h',\r\n    }\r\n    MAP_REV = {\r\n        v: k for k, v in MAP.items()\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    @classmethod\r\n    def decode_body(cls, buf: memoryview) -> str:\r\n        data = cls.MAP_REV.get(buf.tobytes())\r\n        if data is not None:\r\n            return data\r\n        else:\r\n            raise errors.ProtoDecodeError(f'Cannot decode byte: {buf!r}')\r\n\r\n    @classmethod\r\n    def encode_body(cls, data: str)  -> bytes:\r\n        compressed = cls.MAP.get(data)\r\n        if compressed is not None:\r\n            return compressed\r\n        else:\r\n            raise errors.ProtoEncodeError(f'Cannot encode string: {data!r}')\r\n```\r\n\r\n\u4f7f\u7528\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u53d1\u9001\u6d88\u606f:\r\n```python\r\ncli.send_msg('S', 'Hello World')\r\n```\r\n\u5c06\u4f1a\u5728\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u63a5\u6536\u5230\u6d88\u606f `Hello World`\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "dip.const", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "dip.const.IS_WINDOWS", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "dip.errors", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "dip.errors.DeepFOSError", "bases": ["Exception"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Base exception for this package"]}, {"name": "dip.errors.ProtocolError", "bases": ["DeepFOSError"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Base exception related to protocol"]}, {"name": "dip.errors.DeepFOSIOError", "bases": ["DeepFOSError"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Base exception related to I/O"]}, {"name": "dip.errors.DuplicateProtoError", "bases": ["ProtocolError"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Duplicated message type found in registered protocl"]}, {"name": "dip.errors.UnsupportedProtoError", "bases": ["ProtocolError"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Unknown protocol"]}, {"name":